---
title: Fattoush-Inspired Chicken Breast Salad with Spiced Pitas and Feta Cheese
description: From our beloved shawarma spice blend to the crispy pita and chickpeas, everything about this salad delights! Our version of this Mediterranean fried bread salad is also layered with a roasted garlic dressing and tossed with herbs, fresh veg and chicken.
